description: Number of modules with n elements over ring Z[ sqrt(10) ].
references: P. Samuel, Theorie algebrique des nombres, Hermann Editeurs.
D. Zagier, Zetafunktionen und quadratische Koerper, Springer-Verlag.
formula: Define chi(n)=0 if n=2; legendre(10, n) if n is odd prime; chi(p1)^e1 * ... * chi(pk)^ek if n = p1^e1 * ... * pk^ek; Dirichlet g.f.: sum( a(n) / n^s, n=1..inf) = prod ( Z(ms), m=1..inf)
author: Paolo Dominici (pl.dm(AT)libero.it)
